               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183503020117"></xptr>
               <p>Manchester-square. On the 21st of February, I was standing at the door—I saw the prisoner run by, and snatch a counterpane off a table at the door—I ran after him, and called "Stop thief"—I am sure he is the man—he was brought back by the policeman, and Mr. Banister in Duke-street—the policeman had the counterpane under his arm.</p>
               <p>
